Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:52.01,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur6}感受这炽热
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:56.14,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur6}撩动感官  刺激的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:02:01.39,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur6}导火线的去向交由风定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:04.06,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur6}此即命运的倒计时
